title: POLICE AND WOMEN MINISTRY TO SIGN A MOU (Government of the Republic of Fiji)
text: ( Source : Government of the Republic of Fiji ) 10/8/ 2015 A new Memorandum of Understanding ( MOU ) will be signed between the Fiji Police Force and the Ministry of Women , Children and Poverty Alleviation in November this year. Minister , Hon.
